                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Can be combined with Speed Trigger , Spring-Loaded Chamber , Vigilante Fervor and Primed Shred to provide a 330% ( 660% for Bows) increase in fire rate while aiming, otherwise 255% ( 510% for bows)"
