                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Compared to only a maxed rank Serration, adding a Vile Acceleration represents a loss of only 5.6% damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Vile Acceleration",
                  "pageId": 572615,
                  "revisionId": 2780216,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "With a max ranked Serration (but without Heavy Caliber ), this represents a DPS upgrade over Speed Trigger of about 12% on fully automatic weapons that can take full advantage of the fire rate increase. It does still lead to greater ammo consumption and more frequent reloads though, so keep that in mind when modding your weapon."
                }
